Class StudioManagerController

java.lang.Object
fitnessclubjavafx.StudioManagerController
public class StudioManagerController extends Object
This is controller for the Studio Manager GUI. Allows for user inputs to manage the fitness club functionalities. Handles onClick functionalities for GUI Nodes/Buttons
Author:
Ved Patel, Vivek Manthri

    • timeConflictChecker

      private boolean timeConflictChecker(FitnessClass targetClass, Profile profile, Instructor instructor, Location studio, Member member)
      Helper method to check for time conflicts based on classes a member may be in at the same time
      Parameters:
      targetClass - the target FitnessClass in which the member may be in
      profile - the profile of the member
      instructor - the instructor of the class
      studio - the studio location of the class
      member - the member whose time conflicts are checked
      Returns:
      true if the member is currently in a class held at the same time; false if no time conflicts
